snippet.title: Maskonauts: Chat'Attack is coming to Steam!
snippet.description:
Shoot and loot the content of your favorite Twitch channels with Maskonauts: Chat'Attack!

Play it now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2139730/Maskonauts_ChatAttack/

Get in your Maskopod and play in real time with Twitch chats activities! 
Survive waves of texts, Emoticodes and enemies. 
Collect bonuses and try to defeat the Blockbossters and save the Maskotios!

Follow us on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/quantybandit
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/quantybandit/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/quantybandit
Our website: https://quantybandit.com/
